  "title": "HUMAN RESOURCE (HR) MANAGER",
  "description": "<ul><li>To handle all Work Permit related matters ie application / renewal / cancellation / replacement of Work Pass etc.</li><li>To liaise with government authority ie MOM pertaining to worker matters.</li><li>Posting job openings and managing job advertisements, reviewing and shortlisting resumes, conducting interviews and selecting suitable candidates, onboarding new employees.</li><li>Workers’ Payroll Administration.</li><li>To handle workers’ matters ie training arrangement, prepare contracts, home leave arrangement, dormitory administration, worker insurance, petty cash submission etc.</li><li>To liaise with government authority ie MOM pertaining to worker matters.</li><li>Other ad-hoc admin duties.</li><li>Planning for company welfare.</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <a href=\"mailto:davidnhbsg@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com</strong></a><strong>;ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com;</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p>",
